data.description: Lovely ranch home in a quiet country setting on a large 2.11 acres corner lot with a circular driveway .  Very well maintained with new roof replaced in 2022. This home has a lot to offer. 2 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms. Granite counter tops and island in the kitchen. Beautiful hard wood floors through out. It includes a huge heated and cooled sunroom and a large covered patio that invites you over to the backyard oasis, where you can either go in the hot tub or the above ground pool. Also has a carport and a 21x34 wired detached garage. This is a must see. Sunroom 540 sq ft not permitted.
